Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:08.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥 回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:12.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等一下 我今天是值日生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼啊笨蛋粟屋 我幫你做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:18.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦快點回去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:20.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,記得恩恩愛愛地順路去一下可麗餅店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:24.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小繪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:27.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火 現在要回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:28.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:29.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:32.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那要不要一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:36.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,升上二年級也不常一起回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:37.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.38,0:00:39.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:43.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊最近是和粟屋一起回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:44.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:46.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.64,0:00:49.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟 是男朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:51.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,男友優先
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:55.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 多謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:01:00.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 粟屋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:03.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,粟屋也很受歡迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:05.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的挺相襯的不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:12.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不和朋友一起回去好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:15.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 給我喝一口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:30.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:34.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇…了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:40.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:44.00,Kuzu_title1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HE1\t(0,930,0.5,\alpha&H00)\fs150\blur30\t(0,930,2.5,\blur0)\t(0,3000,0.8,\fs105)\pos(1272,585)}有求於那份溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,--------------OP----------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:19.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥和我是住在同一座公寓的青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:22.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:27.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小乃莉子和麥君在一起的話就像公主殿下和王子殿下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:32.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下和王子殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:37.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這句話把年幼的我俘虜住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:44.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,升上一年級我留長了頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:47.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,變得不再和男孩子一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:50.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是收集很多可愛的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:53.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想要成為配得上王子的公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:58.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來 明明只要王子回頭來看我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:00.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這一切就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:04.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是鷗端乃莉子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:09.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:10.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:14.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是 安樂岡花火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:16.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:19.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:23.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…我想起你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:26.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 你認識？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:29.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 鷗鷗鴨鷗來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:30.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太多鷗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 乃莉子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:34.25,kuzu_scene6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs105\fad(50,0)\pos(169,563)\c&H464648&}乃莉子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:34.25,kuzu_scene6,,0,0,0,,{\c&H353535&\fs60\fad(50,0)\pos(42,750)}(真名)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:34.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個你倒是記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:36.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,鷗端最可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:39.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我名字寫作最可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:41.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:42.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別的我都不接受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:47.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是是 還是一如既往的麻煩啊你這人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:52.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是 從以前開始就超讓人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:55.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼像你這種人會和麥拍拖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:58.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥也被這種女人騙了真可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:05:01.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在麥面前也是在裝可愛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:02.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒裝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:04.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 居然發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:08.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 這傢伙品行惡劣 頗為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:10.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真不想被你說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:13.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼啊這
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:18.42,kuzu_scene6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord9\fs105\frz286.2\fad(294,0)\3c&H386CC9&\move(-54,420,208.5,420,0,3089)}感覺真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:18.42,kuzu_scene6,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs105\frz286.2\move(-54,420,208.5,420,0,3089)\fad(294,0)\3c&HFFFFFF&}感覺真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:18.42,kuzu_scene6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord9\frz286.2\move(-214.5,717,48,717,0,3089)\fad(294,0)}{\fs105\3c&H386CC9&}那種語氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:18.42,kuzu_scene6,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\frz286.2\move(-214.5,717,48,717,0,3089)\fad(294,0)\fs105\3c&HFFFFFF&}那種語氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:19.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 這也是花火她的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:25.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 我也是喜歡麥的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:34.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以請不要未經許可就去勾搭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:37.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:44.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天的 那傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不用做到這程度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:52.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那人喜歡你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:54.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:59.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不如說 為什麼不好好甩掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:04.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是完全沒用那種心思去看她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:06.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是溫柔的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:07.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:10.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是因為那人可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:12.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:14.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:16.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:18.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是沉浸於優越感裡而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:22.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在奇怪的地方抬槓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:27.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對我有獨占欲嗎 嫉妒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別誤會了笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:33.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,與占有慾…不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:36.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:39.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的只是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:42.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:47.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都太拼命了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:58.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太奇怪了啊日本的通勤列車
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:04.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好想快點見到麥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:10.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能想念著麥的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是最為痛苦並讓人討厭的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:16.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,漸漸地在自己心中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:24.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不經意地按自己的欲望改寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:25.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:35.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最可今天也吃麵包？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:38.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:41.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,給 甜的和不甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:43.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不說也想要的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:46.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:48.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛 給我放開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:52.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:52.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 真正見面的時間才是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:55.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為此才會有現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 便當
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:04.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有炸雞喔 吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:04.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:07.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來 啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:13.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,炸雞塊消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:17.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真的啊 靈異現象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:19.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們 別無視我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:20.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,給我適可而唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:24.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我才要說你給我適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:25.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然敢恬不知恥地在午餐時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:28.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像情侶般旁若無人地跟過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:31.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前忠告過你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:33.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真吵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:35.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,野獸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:40.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這性格惡劣的女人 你絕對不是有多喜歡麥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:42.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被利用了啊麥你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:43.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對那女人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:46.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是與帥氣的麥在一起就洋洋得意之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:47.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:49.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:52.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 虧你能發現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:54.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們 不要都給我同意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:59.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 我是絕對不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:00.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:03.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不放棄就別逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:05.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:07.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,用的還是敬語
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:09.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真不爽 真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,利用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:21.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在走廊上跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:22.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直想說一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:29.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,走廊可不能跑啊這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:31.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像電視劇動畫裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:35.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個為什麼我非得幫忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:39.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思讓小花以外的人幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:42.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法啊真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:46.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 要搬到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到國語準備室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:51.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 不就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:55.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:59.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,機會 不是獨自興奮的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:00.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}講義就放在那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 我應該做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:04.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 真重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:07.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,至少要讓哥哥意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:09.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是作為一名「異性」存在的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:25.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,鋼琴聲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:34.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:36.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,彈得真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:39.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,經常都能聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:51.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都成為音樂老師了會彈個鋼琴不是理所當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:54.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別用麥克風說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:57.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如此下去一無所有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:11:01.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有與你甘苦與共
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:04.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,終於我們才會意識
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:08.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那些就已經是全……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:06.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不想放棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:14.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺更年輕更帥氣的大有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:16.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:19.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是在說我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥你也來唱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:30.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,動搖的心化為洶湧的旋渦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:33.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相互融解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:38.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相互融解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:42.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:47.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥是很帥的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:51.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:57.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:12:00.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂的吧 麥你也一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:04.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是放棄不放棄的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:09.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡上一個人 便是非他不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:10.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:16.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:18.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼喜歡上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不都是痛苦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:26.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:32.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不會去想「要是不認識的話」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:35.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:39.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:41.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被稱作多餘的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:47.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:50.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,舌頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:51.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:12.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,粟屋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:19.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,粟屋 摸一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:24.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:32.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 叫哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 也對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:47.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小麥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:53.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然用你來幻想這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,並因此感到心安理得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:06.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,索性 你能夠痛斥我一頓就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:18.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,性格惡劣的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:21.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你絕對不是有多喜歡麥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥只是被你利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:27.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,利用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:39.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被利用的是 花火的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:45.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小繪 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:50.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了花火 你滿臉通紅的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,睡過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是完全還來得及嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:56.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:11.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛諮詢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:17.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好的嘛 偶爾這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:18.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看唄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:22.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要說什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:25.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火你沒什麼女性朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:27.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有 有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:30.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都說有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:32.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比如說？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:35.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小 小繪等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:37.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只有她一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:41.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才叫你去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:42.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:49.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要接吻了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:54.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:57.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:01.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:02.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,搞得像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:07.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像是真正的男朋友一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:14.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天想找你諮詢的是她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:19.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這位步美同學和宏是青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他們家住的很近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:23.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到國中時兩人就順理成章的交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:29.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然當時還許下要永遠在一起這種天真的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:30.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:31.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:32.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,後來他們上了不同的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:34.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小宏輕易的就劈腿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:36.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是步美卻無法放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:39.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至自己提出那樣也無所謂的備胎宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:42.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這時跟步美同學校的學長注意到了這個情況
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:42.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:47.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,步美漸漸的被學長的溫柔所俘獲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:51.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但果然還是沒辦法跟宏斷絕關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:55.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,結果就和宏還有學長同時保持著關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:57.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:00.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就和小宏的作為一樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:02.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:05.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說了讓她選學長的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:07.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安樂岡也是這樣想的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:12.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 這劇情好複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:15.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,步美到底喜歡哪一方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我決定不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:22.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,決定不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:23.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:26.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能和哥哥進展順利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就能和麥分手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:30.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥也是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:34.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺對她們的話題沒有共鳴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:38.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 叫你選學長啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:40.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼看都是學長條件更好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:42.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:46.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真的對兩人都喜歡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:48.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,並因此感到痛苦的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:50.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還是都分手斬斷痛苦比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:58.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,應該說是因為兩個人都喜歡才感到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.38,0:18:02.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說因為沒辦法決定才感覺痛苦之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:05.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想自己選錯人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:07.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:09.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想之後再後悔嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:12.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是選學長比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:15.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是小宏更帥嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,考慮到將來的話還是前輩比較好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:20.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小宏的優點就只會運動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:22.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,換成安樂岡同學會選誰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:26.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 小繪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:35.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:40.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小繪有喜歡的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:44.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼突然問這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:46.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看來有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:53.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小繪不會因為那個人的條件好壞而喜歡上那個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:05.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個的話 能力也是那個人的一部分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:09.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不會因為那個人很優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:13.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能給自己帶來好處而喜歡上他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小繪～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:18.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我還是最喜歡小繪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:22.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:23.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:26.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡一個人才不是那樣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟花火有男朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:38.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小繪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:41.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要來我家留宿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:43.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:50.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:51.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:55.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我會在做過夜的準備啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:59.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小繪好像也有喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:04.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們倆乾脆來個通宵girls talk怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:05.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:09.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會在同一張床上睡覺什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.47,0:20:19.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊，結果只是跟小繪關係好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:24.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,囉嗦 有小繪就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:31.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都是女生 不知道有什麼打算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:33.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,女生聚會？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:34.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:39.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:45.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:51.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為都是女生 才能那麼隨意的在彼此家中留宿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能比平時更靠近她一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:57.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不就夠幸運的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:00.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 樂觀點樂觀點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:04.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:08.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是那樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:09.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:10.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:13.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還是做了這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:17.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:19.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,乾脆死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我這種人
